### Issue 6: Card Link Opens in New Tab Without User Control (Line 82)

**Line:** 82  
**Code:**
```js
btn.target = "_blank";
```

**Problem:** All card CTA buttons force `target="_blank"`. On the **Sightseeing** card, the link goes to the same domain (`goindigo.in/sightseeing`). Opening same-domain pages in a new tab after a booking confirmation breaks the navigation flow — the user expects to continue within the same session.

**Solution:** Make `target` configurable per card, defaulting to `_self` for same-domain links:
```js
btn.target = data.target || "_self";
btn.rel = data.target === "_blank" ? "noopener noreferrer" : "";
```

